replies.body:
I got to play one Ascension game as him. I went with the Classic skin so that I could tell the enemy Galactic Azir that he was "The Kang to my Rama-Tut. I am older. Wiser." And incidentally, Nasus was on *my* team so it made our narrow victory all the more appropriate.

Yeah that was a nerdy reference! And I'm proud! {{champion:74}}

Anyway, he was super exciting to play and so my tears flow alongside yours.
